[The experience with the early rehabilitation of the children presenting with 
the vertebral cerebrospinal injury].

[Article in Russian; Abstract available in Russian from the publisher]

Roshal LM(1), Novoselova IN(1), Valiullina SA(1), Ponina IV(1), Machalov VA(1), 
Vasilieva MF(1), Lukjanov VI(1).

Author information:
(1)State budgetary healthcare facility 'Clinical and Research Institute of 
